				<td colspan="2"><span>We are in serious need of some DPS. It has been said many times that we need a boost of our DPS, especially with the OOW song downgrades.
<br />

<br />
What about a back stab AA? It would not be anything as nice as what the rogues have of course but just somehthing, maybe a quarter or half what the rogues get. Make it 66+ too. We are at least partially rogues, we sneak, hide, do traps... all not quite as well as rogues but we do OK.. 
<br />

<br />
I think that would make us useful again.</span></td>
