<br />

<br />
The reason I would favor BS over a straight melee increase is the flash factor.  Push the button, hit something for a bit of damage with your name attached to it.  People don't notice things unless its in their face, like necros feeling overshadowed because only they can see thier dot spam.  BS would be a nice &quot;Hey, look at me, I critted for 400!&quot;  ego stroke, that could also be used to bump our DPS to the magic .65.  h*ll it doesn't have to be backstab, but a nice, flashy bump to our damage potential would be nice.  I just like backstab because it helps to bring us closer RP wise to our rogish heritage then Advanced_Bellow_01</span></td>
